poispkgs

An R package to install and attach CRAN and GitHub Packages used in Poisson Consulting analyses.

Demonstration

Installation

To install the latest development version from the Poisson drat repository including all dependencies

install.packages("drat")
drat::addRepo("poissonconsulting", dependencies = TRUE)
install.packages("poispkgs")
